  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="badge">AGR</div>
      <div>
        <h1>Agriculture — 10 Business Ideas for Nidavellir</h1>
        <p class="lead">Each idea includes a concise description and key features you can expand into a Phase‑3 business case.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid">

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">1. AgroSense Irrigation Grid</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">Smart, sensor-driven irrigation platform that optimizes water use across farms and orchards.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Soil moisture sensors + weather API for automated watering</li>
          <li>Mobile dashboard for farmers and water-usage billing</li>
          <li>Water-saving schedules and alert system</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">2. CropEye Drone Patrol</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">Drone monitoring service for crop health, disease detection and yield estimation using multispectral imaging.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Periodic drone flights with automated reports</li>
          <li>Early pest/disease alerts and prescription recommendations</li>
          <li>Subscription pricing for smallholder bundles</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">3. Farm2City Connect</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">Direct B2B/B2C supply chain linking farmers to markets and restaurants, cutting out middlemen.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Pre-booked consignments and transparent pricing</li>
          <li>Cold-chain partners and scheduled pickups</li>
          <li>Digital contracts & payment settlement</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">4. EcoFert BioUnit</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">Local biofertiliser and compost production from agricultural and city organic waste.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Decentralised compost hubs near farming clusters</li>
          <li>Training for farmers on organic input use</li>
          <li>Buy-back & subscription supply models</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">5. ColdNest Agro Storage</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">Temperature-controlled storage and post-harvest handling to reduce spoilage and extend market window.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Modular cold rooms with pay-per-use pricing</li>
          <li>Inventory tracking and release-on-demand</li>
          <li>Integrated logistics to retailers</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">6. GreenHarvest Organic Farm</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">A flagship organic farming unit producing chemical-free vegetables and herbs for premium markets.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Certified organic cultivation & traceability</li>
          <li>CSA boxes (subscription deliveries) to city residents</li>
          <li>Farm visits and agritourism tie-ins with resort</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">7. AgroLabs & Training Centre</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">On-site lab and extension services providing soil tests, seed trials and farmer training programs.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Rapid soil & water diagnostics</li>
          <li>Demonstration plots and pilot trials</li>
          <li>Workshops for sustainable practices</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">8. AgriFin Microloan Platform</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">Financial services tailored for farmers — crop loans, insurance tie-ups, and microcredit for inputs.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Pay-as-you-harvest repayment schedules</li>
          <li>Insurance bundles against weather risk</li>
          <li>Mobile KYC and disbursement</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">9. PolliGuard Pest Control</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">Integrated pest management service using pheromone traps, biopesticides and predictive analytics.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Low-chemical, eco-friendly methods</li>
          <li>Advisory via SMS & app alerts</li>
          <li>Seasonal subscription with on-field visits</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="name"><strong class="title">10. AgriHub Digital Marketplace</strong></div>
        <p class="desc">A farmer-centric online marketplace for seeds, tools, services and B2B buyers with traceability features.</p>
        <div class="meta">Key features:</div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Verified sellers & quality ratings</li>
          <li>Integrated logistics & payment</li>
          <li>Knowledge base and peer reviews</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

    </div>

